Detailed Description

Author
Hans Joachim Ferreau, Andreas Potschka, Christian Kirches
Version
3.1embedded
Date
2007-2015

Implementation of the Indexlist class designed to manage index lists of constraints and bounds within a QProblem_SubjectTo.
